        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "In these temptations Levi had proved itself \"a holy one,\" although in the latter Moses and Aaron stumbled, since the Levites had risen up in defence of the honour of the Lord and had kept His covenant, even with the denial of father, mother, brethren, and children (",
